#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:146
msgid ""
"The A3 resource pool has a maximum concurrency of **5×16 NPUs**. Multi-"
"node tests run with `max-parallel: 2` to avoid resource exhaustion. "
"Running `/nightly all` on A3 will queue a large number of jobs — prefer "
"targeting specific test names when possible."
msgstr "A3 资源池的最大并发量为 **5×16 NPU**。多节点测试以 `max-parallel: 2` 运行以避免资源耗尽。在 A3 上运行 `/nightly all` 会排队大量作业——在可能的情况下，请优先指定具体的测试名称。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:152
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:154
msgid "Run all available nightly tests against your PR:"
msgstr "针对你的 PR 运行所有可用的夜间测试："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:160
msgid "Run only the custom operator single-card test:"
msgstr "仅运行自定义算子单卡测试："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:166
msgid "Run two specific tests at once:"
msgstr "同时运行两个特定测试："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:172
msgid ""
"Re-trigger after fixing an issue: just push a new commit. The "
"`synchronize` event re-runs the workflow and picks up the existing "
"`/nightly` comment automatically — no need to post a new comment."
msgstr "修复问题后重新触发：只需推送一个新的提交。`synchronize` 事件会重新运行工作流，并自动拾取现有的 `/nightly` 评论——无需发布新评论。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:176
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "故障排除"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:178
msgid "**The workflow didn't start after I added the label.**"
msgstr "**添加标签后工作流没有启动。**"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:180
msgid ""
"Make sure the `/nightly` comment was posted **before** the label was "
"added. If the label was added first, remove it and re-add it after "
"posting the comment."
msgstr "确保 `/nightly` 评论是在添加标签**之前**发布的。如果先添加了标签，请移除它，并在发布评论后重新添加。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:182
msgid ""
"Check that the comment starts exactly with `/nightly` with no leading "
"spaces or extra characters before the slash."
msgstr "检查评论是否恰好以 `/nightly` 开头，斜杠前没有前导空格或额外字符。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:184
msgid ""
"To re-trigger after fixing an issue, simply push a new commit — the "
"workflow will reuse the existing `/nightly` comment automatically."
msgstr "要在修复问题后重新触发，只需推送一个新的提交——工作流会自动重用现有的 `/nightly` 评论。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:187
msgid "**Only some tests ran, not the ones I expected.**"
msgstr "**只运行了部分测试，不是我预期的那些。**"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:189
msgid ""
"Test names are case-sensitive and must match the `name` field in the "
"workflow matrix exactly (see the table above)."
msgstr "测试名称区分大小写，并且必须与工作流矩阵中的 `name` 字段完全匹配（参见上表）。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:191
msgid ""
"Check the `parse-trigger` job output in GitHub Actions for the resolved "
"`test_filter` value."
msgstr "在 GitHub Actions 中检查 `parse-trigger` 作业的输出，查看解析后的 `test_filter` 值。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:194
msgid "**The workflow ran with the scheduled image, not my PR code.**"
msgstr "**工作流运行的是预定镜像，而不是我的 PR 代码。**"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:196
msgid ""
"Confirm the workflow was triggered by a `pull_request` event (label or "
"push), not `workflow_dispatch`."
msgstr "确认工作流是由 `pull_request` 事件（标签或推送）触发的，而不是 `workflow_dispatch`。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:198
msgid "The `parse-trigger` job logs show `is_pr_event` — check its value."
msgstr "`parse-trigger` 作业日志会显示 `is_pr_event`——检查其值。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:200
msgid ""
"**How to obtain more detailed logs to pinpoint problems for multi-node "
"tests**"
msgstr "**如何获取更详细的日志以定位多节点测试的问题**"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:202
msgid ""
"For most issues, the stdout pop-up logs from GitHub actions are "
"sufficient (this log always represents the logs from the first node)."
msgstr "对于大多数问题，GitHub Actions 的 stdout 弹出日志已足够（此日志始终代表第一个节点的日志）。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/contribution/nightly_ci_test.md:203
msgid ""
"If the logs from a first node are no longer sufficient to provide "
"effective logging information, see the summary of your jobs to download "
"log archive for the corresponding test, which includes the framework-side"
" logs and plog information for each node, structured as follows:"
msgstr "如果第一个节点的日志已不足以提供有效的日志信息，请查看作业摘要以下载相应测试的日志归档，其中包含框架端日志和每个节点的 plog 信息，结构如下："
